<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Workflow invitation</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body style="background-color: #f1f2f3; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;">
  <div style="text-align: center; padding: 50px 0;">
    <a href="https://www.wouvy.fr"><img src="{{path.logo}}" alt="Logo" style="height: 70px; filter: grayscale(100%);" /></a>
  </div>
  <div style="background-color: #ffffff; width: 60%; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 30px; padding: 50px; box-shadow: 0 0 15px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 10px;">
      <img src="{{path.elliot}}" alt="Elliot" style="height: 60px;" />
    </div>
    <h3 style="text-align: center; text-decoration: none; font-size: 26px; color: #3f4147; margin-bottom: 15px;">{{userName}} vous invite à rejoindre son Workflow.</h3>
    <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px; color: #677077;">Rejoignez-le en quelques clics et communiquez plus rapidement !</p>
    <div style="margin: 30px 0 10px; text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{workflowAccessLink}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px; font-size: 16px; border-radius: 20px; background-color: #ffd91b; color: white; text-decoration: none; box-shadow: 0 0 80px 5px rgba(255, 211, 31, 0.4);">
        <span style="text-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);">Rejoindre</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="text-align:center; padding: 30px 0 60px;">
    <a href="https://www.wouvy.fr/" style="font-size:14px; color: #d1d1d1; padding: 0 10px;">Mentions légales</a>
    <a href="https://www.wouvy.fr/" style="font-size:14px; color: #d1d1d1; padding: 0 10px; border-left: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-right: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">Wouvy, qu'est ce que c'est ?</a>
    <a href="https://www.wouvy.fr/" style="font-size:14px; color: #d1d1d1; padding: 0 10px;">CGUV</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
